OL,3,CLast Falklands era warship given
OL,4,C'respectful farewell' as it heads to
OL,5,Cscrapyard
OL,7,FVeterans and members of the public
OL,8,Fhave turned out to give a "respectful
OL,9,Ffarewell" to a former Royal Navy
OL,10,Fflagship that played a "vital role" in
OL,11,Fthe Falklands conflict.
OL,13,FHMS Bristol was towed out of
OL,14,FPortsmouth Harbour on Wednesday,
OL,15,Falmost five years after it was
OL,16,Fdecommissioned.
OL,18,FThe warship, which was the last ship
OL,19,Fserving from the Falklands war, is
OL,20,Fbeing taken to a Turkish scrapyard.
