OL,7,FThe Type 82 destroyer was commissioned
OL,8,Fin March 1973 but having been designed
OL,9,Fto defend a class of aircraft carriers
OL,10,Fwhich was never built, it was the only
OL,11,Fwarship of its class to enter service.
OL,13,FBristol led a group of two destroyers,
OL,14,Ffive frigates and an RFA supply ship
OL,15,Fproviding reinforcements in the
OL,16,FFalklands war and later joined the
OL,17,Fcarrier battle task group as an air
OL,18,Fdefence destroyer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
