OL,7,FIn 1987 it became a training ship as
OL,8,Fpart of the Dartmouth Training
OL,9,FSquadron before an explosion in its
OL,10,Fboiler led to it being used as a
OL,11,Fharbour training vessel at HMS
OL,12,FExcellent, Portsmouth, until it was
OL,13,Fdecommissioned in October 2020 after
OL,14,Fnearly 48 years of service.
OL,16,FMembers of the public and veterans
OL,17,Fcongregated on Old Portsmouth's Round
OL,18,FTower to wave off Bristol, which was
OL,19,Fvisually rust-stained, as it left the
OL,20,FHampshire naval base.
