OL,3,CLast Falklands era warship given
OL,4,C'respectful farewell' as it heads to
OL,5,Cscrapyard
OL,7,FChris Howe, of the South Atlantic
OL,8,FMedal Association 1982, said: "As HMS
OL,9,FBristol embarks on its final voyage to
OL,10,Fthe scrapyard in Turkey, we pause to
OL,11,Freflect on its remarkable and unique
OL,12,Flegacy.
OL,14,F"This ship played a vital role in the
OL,15,F1982 Falklands conflict, serving as a
OL,16,Fheadquarters and providing steadfast
OL,17,Fsupport to British forces.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
