OL,3,CLast Falklands era warship given
OL,4,C'respectful farewell' as it heads to
OL,5,Cscrapyard
OL,7,F"For many veterans, Bristol was more
OL,8,Fthan a vessel ` it was a home, a place
OL,9,Fof camaraderie, and a symbol of
OL,10,Fresilience.
OL,12,F"Its departure marks the end of an
OL,13,Fera, but its contributions to our
OL,14,Fhistory and the memories of those who
OL,15,Fserved aboard will endure.
OL,17,F"We honour all who sailed in her and
OL,18,Fbid HMS Bristol a respectful farewell."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
