OL,4,C'respectful farewell' as it heads to
OL,5,Cscrapyard
OL,7,FHMS Bristol was sold for recycling by
OL,8,Fship recycling experts from the
OL,9,FDefence Equipment & Support (DE&S)
OL,10,FDefence Recycling & Disposals Team
OL,11,F(DRDT), on behalf of the Royal Navy.
OL,13,FA DE&S spokesman said it would be
OL,14,Ftaken to a specialist recycling
OL,15,Ffacility within an EU-approved yard in
OL,16,FTurkey, with all reusable equipment
OL,17,Fhaving been removed for sale.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
