OL,3,CLast Falklands era warship given
OL,4,C'respectful farewell' as it heads to
OL,5,Cscrapyard
OL,7,FAlistair Hughes, head of DRDT, said:
OL,8,F"Recycling of ships at the end of
OL,9,Ftheir hull life is routine business
OL,10,Ffor the Royal Navy and our aim is to
OL,11,Fachieve maximum value for money for
OL,12,Fdefence in an environmentally
OL,13,Fcompliant manner ` HMS Bristol is a
OL,14,Ffitting example of this after her many
OL,15,Fdedicated years of service."
